Title: A Study of Atezolizumab (an Engineered Anti-Programmed Death-Ligand 1 [PD-L1] Antibody) as Monotherapy or in Combination With Bevacizumab (Avastin®) Compared to Sunitinib (Sutent®) in Participants With Untreated Advanced Renal Cell Carcinoma
Conditions: Renal Cell Carcinoma
Phase: PHASE2
Status: COMPLETED
Primary outcomes: Percentage of Participants With Disease Progression Per Response Evaluation Criteria in Solid Tumors Version 1.1 (RECIST v1.1) Via Independent Review Committee (IRC) Assessment or Death in Intent-to-Treat (ITT) Population; Progression-Free Survival (PFS) Per RECIST v1.1 Via IRC Assessment in ITT Population; Percentage of Participants With Disease Progression Per RECIST v1.1 Via IRC Assessment or Death in Immune Cell 1/2/3 (IC1/2/3) Population; PFS Per RECIST v1.1 Via IRC Assessment in IC1/2/3 Population